description: Registers a set of tag keys to include in scheduled event notifications for your resources. To remove tags, use DeregisterInstanceEventNotificationAttributes.

parameters.name: InstanceTagAttribute
parameters.description: Information about the tag keys to register. IncludeAllTagsOfInstance (boolean) --- Indicates whether to register all tag keys in the current Region. Specify true to register all tag keys. InstanceTagKeys (list) --- The tag keys to register. (string) ---

nested_params.name: IncludeAllTagsOfInstance
nested_params.description: Indicates whether to register all tag keys in the current Region. Specify true to register all tag keys.

nested_items.name: InstanceTagAttribute
nested_items.description: The resulting set of tag keys.

nested_items.name: IncludeAllTagsOfInstance
nested_items.description: Indicates wheter all tag keys in the current Region are registered to appear in scheduled event notifications. true indicates that all tag keys in the current Region are registered.
